### 3.2 Facility Manager Functional Requirements

| ID | Name | Description |
|----|------|-------------|
| FR-FM-01 | Account Creation | The system shall allow a Facility Manager to create an account. |
| FR-FM-02 | User Authentication | The system shall allow a Facility Manager to log in using a valid email and password. |
| FR-FM-03 | Manager Dashboard | The system shall provide managers with a dashboard to view all tickets and their statuses. |
| FR-FM-04 | Assign Worker | The system shall allow managers to assign a ticket to a worker. |
