## 5. Constraints

| ID | Constraint | Description |
|----|------------|-------------|
| C-01 | Time | The project must be completed within the academic semester timeline. All development, testing, and documentation must be finalized before the final submission deadline. |
| C-02 | Budget | The project must rely only on free or student-accessible tools and services. Paid infrastructure or premium cloud services are out of scope. |
| C-03 | Resources | The system will be designed and implemented by a team of six students, limiting development, testing, and maintenance capacity. |
| C-04 | Technology | The project must use React Native, Node.js, and PostgreSQL as specified in course guidelines. |
| C-05 | Infrastructure | The system will be hosted on free-tier cloud platforms, which may impose limits on storage, processing power, and concurrent users. |
| C-06 | Testing | Testing will be conducted on available student devices and emulators, limiting coverage across all device types and OS versions. |
| C-07 | Internet Dependency | The system requires an internet connection. Some functionality may be limited when the device is offline. |

