## 8. Future Scope

1. **Integrated Communication Module (In-App Messaging):** A commenting system within ticket details will allow workers and managers to exchange technical notes or progress updates directly on a specific ticket, reducing reliance on external communication tools.

2. **Intelligent Duplicate Detection:** A "Nearby Issues" warning will alert users if a similar issue at the same location has already been reported, preventing redundant submissions.

3. **Management Analytics Dashboard:** An administrative reporting tool with data visualizations for "Average Time to Resolution" and "Top Maintenance Categories" to help allocate campus resources effectively.

4. **Real-Time Emergency Notifications:** Leveraging Expo Push Notification service to send instant high-priority alerts to workers for Urgent or Sustainability-related issues (e.g., water leaks, fire hazards).